00:24:18,416 --> 00:24:28,375
♪

591
00:24:28,458 --> 00:24:38,375
♪

592
00:24:38,458 --> 00:24:48,375
♪

593
00:24:48,458 --> 00:24:58,666
♪

594
00:24:58,750 --> 00:25:01,500
[MIYUKI] Suzuhara
can't defend herself!

595
00:25:01,583 --> 00:25:02,708
[IZUMIKO] That's enough, Mayura!

596
00:25:02,791 --> 00:25:04,208
Please don't do this!

